o\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200-metre freestyle\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the Dolphins\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4\\u00d7100-metre freestyle relay\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was another show of strength for Australia.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 960, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9114260471924102, \"rank\": 0.06465342889557107, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another show\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been an awesome few days watching all the Aussies get up and race so I just had to put my best foot forward tonight,\\\" said McKeown, who now owns four Olympic golds and will aim for another in the 200-metre backstroke.\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an awesome few days\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Aussies\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"my best foot\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"McKeown\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"four Olympic golds\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200-metre backstroke\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To have all this atmosphere, all that adrenaline and be able to perform like, that it's really special to me and I am happy with having gone so far,\\\" she said She is now one of only two women, along with American Natalie Coughlin, to have won two golds in this event.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\"